Package: TrajectoryMarkovAnalysis
Type: Package
Title: Package for creating Markov models for patient-orientated trajectories. 
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-01-18
Author: Markus Haug
Maintainer: Markus Haug <haugmarkus@protonmail.com>
Description: R-package TrajectoryMarkovAnalysis specializes on modelling patient trajectories using Markov chains. The package supports discrete and continuous time Markov models, Kaplan-Meier plots, Markov trees and synthetic data generation. The package is based on OMOP CDM.
